"title": "9145: Messianic age",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9145",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>In the OT, writers look forward to the era that will be inaugurated by God's decisive intervention in human history, in order to establish his eternal kingdom under the Messiah. The Messianic age is characterised by righteousness, justice and peace, by the outpouring of the Holy Spirit and by the restoration and renewal of God's people and of creation. In the NT, the idea appears in a developed form as the “kingdom of God”, inaugurated by the first coming of Jesus Christ and to be consummated at his return.</p>\n<h2>The victory of God's kingdom foreseen</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:37-Dan2:44\">DAN 2:37–2:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:9\">ZEC 14:9</a></p>\n<h3>The victory of God's Messiah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:3-Ps45:6\">PSA 45:3–45:6</a></strong> <em>This psalm came to be applied to the Messiah.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps110:5-Ps110:6\">PSA 110:5–110:6</a> <em>This psalm was also applied to the Messiah in the OT times</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:3-Isa9:5\">ISA 9:3–9:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:13\">ISA 42:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:17-Isa59:19\">ISA 59:17–59:19</a></p>\n<h3>The Messiah's universal reign</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:13-Dan7:14\">DAN 7:13–7:14</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:8-Ps2:9\">PSA 2:8–2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:8-Ps72:11\">PSA 72:8–72:11</a></p>\n<h2>Restoration in the Messianic age</h2>\n<h3>Restoration of harmony in creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:6-Isa11:9\">ISA 11:6–11:9</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:25\">ISA 65:25</a></p>\n<h3>Restoration of the land's prosperity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:13-Amos9:15\">AMO 9:13–9:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:3\">PSA 72:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa4:2\">ISA 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:18\">JOL 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>Restoration and renewal of God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:18\">JER 3:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:6-Mic4:8\">MIC 4:6–4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:1-Isa60:3\">ISA 60:1–60:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:16-Joel3:17\">JOL 3:16–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:11\">AMO 9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:17-Obad1:21\">OBA 1:17–1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:6\">ACT 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:9\">ZEC 3:9</a>HOS <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:5\">3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:4-Jer50:5\">JER 50:4–50:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:19-Ezek11:20\">EZK 11:19–11:20</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:28\">EZK 36:28</a></p>\n<h2>Characteristics of the Messianic age</h2>\n<h3>Righteousness and justice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:1\">ISA 32:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:2\">PSA 72:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:12-Ps72:13\">PSA 72:12–72:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:7\">ISA 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:3-Isa11:5\">ISA 11:3–11:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:16\">ISA 32:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:5-Jer23:6\">JER 23:5–23:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:15-Jer33:16\">JER 33:15–33:16</a></p>\n<h3>Peace and security</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:17-Isa32:18\">ISA 32:17–32:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:3-Mic4:4\">MIC 4:3–4:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:4\">ISA 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:20-Isa65:23\">ISA 65:20–65:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:5-Jer23:6\">JER 23:5–23:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:15-Jer33:16\">JER 33:15–33:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:25-Ezek34:29\">EZK 34:25–34:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9-Zech9:10\">ZEC 9:9–9:10</a></p>\n<h3>Universal acknowledgment of the LORD</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:17\">JER 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:2-Isa2:3\">ISA 2:2–2:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:1-Mic4:2\">MIC 4:1–4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:23-Isa19:25\">ISA 19:23–19:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:16\">ZEC 14:16</a></p>\n<h3>The outpouring of the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:29\">JOL 2:28–2:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:15\">ISA 32:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:3\">ISA 44:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:21\">ISA 59:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:27\">EZK 36:27</a></p>\n<h2>The kingdom of God in the NT</h2>\n<h3>Inaugurated at Jesus Christ's first coming</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:28\">MAT 12:28</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:20\">LUK 11:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:15\">MRK 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:43\">LUK 4:43</a></p>\n<h3>Includes the restoration of all things</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:21\">ACT 3:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1-Rev21:4\">REV 21:1–21:4</a></p>\n<h3>Consummated at Jesus Christ's return</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:15\">REV 11:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30-Matt24:31\">MAT 24:30–24:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:26-Mark13:27\">MRK 13:26–13:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:10\">REV 12:10</a></p>",
